  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a compassionate study to provide continued access to maraviroc for only those
      subjects completing study A4001029 who are showing clinical benefit. Assessments of safety
      and tolerability of maraviroc when added to OBT will be continued.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
